  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The ALCUNA dataset includes 84,351 English queries and 3,554 independently created entities.",
    "Each entity, on average, encompasses 11.75 sets of attribute triples and 25.39 linked entities.",
    "Employing the innovative knowGen technique, adjustments are made to the attributes and relationships of existing entities to produce fresh knowledge.",
    "This process forms the foundation of ALCUNA, designed to evaluate LLMs' proficiency in comprehending, distinguishing, and associating with novel knowledge.",
    "• KoLA (Yu et al, 2023a)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "• KoLA (Yu et al, 2023a)."
  ]
}